item.title: Admin Stuck....Any help would be really APPRECIATED
item.dc:creator: @Narbscape Narbscape
item.description:
@Narbscape wrote:

The reason is because the owner added you to a list in his client.java, sometimes when that happens, the code reads the name, but not the other way.
So ask the owner to make you admin manually, using the character files instead.
